quran[6]{c,v,t,f}:
  7,79,"And he [i.e., Ṣāliḥ] turned away from them and said, "
  7,80,"And [We had sent] Lot when he said to his people, "
  7,81,"Indeed, you approach men with desire, instead of women. Rather, you are a transgressing people."
  8,13,"That is because they opposed Allāh and His Messenger. And whoever opposes Allāh and His Messenger - indeed, Allāh is severe in penalty."
  8,14,""
  8,15,"O you who have believed, when you meet those who disbelieve advancing [in battle], do not turn to them your backs [in flight]."